dataIdInfo.idPurp: The data was created in support of TRecs LIS effort to get an accurate account of UTM building footprints for University print and web campus maps. The data is as up to data as November 2020.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: The data represents UTM building footprint geometry as of November 2020. Includes geo domain, status, building number, building abbreviation, floor, and notes. The data was collected by the TRecs LIS team through field work efforts such as drone scans and lidar scans . The data is visible in UTM campus print/web maps as well as on TRecs AGOL. The data uses NAD_1983_2011_StatePlane_Texas_Central_FIPS_4203_Ft_US coordinate system.

Consts.useLimit: None, this data is authorized as public domain.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

dataLineage.statement: This data comes from the Technology Resources collection and is part of the Basemap collection.
